<?xml version="1.0"?>
<Fleet xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <Name>Azurite Squadron</Name>
  <Version>3</Version>
  <TotalPoints>3000</TotalPoints>
  <FactionKey>Stock/Protectorate</FactionKey>
  <Description>Difficulty: &lt;color=yellow&gt;MODERATE&lt;/color&gt;

Azurite Squadron is an eccentric fleet featuring a revolver lineship, the Abject Terror. With cannons on both sides, revolvers are built to fire their first broadside at a target, barrel roll 180 degrees and unleash the other broadside, then roll again, repeating until the target collapses under the unending rain of shells. Order the closest broadside's weapon group to fire and once it has emptied its clip, cancel the order or use the cease fire command, then issue the order for the other broadside to begin the roll. Azurite also brings along a command cruiser to escort the lineship and provide point defence and fire control as well as additional firepower.
  </Description>
  <SortOverrideOrder>5</SortOverrideOrder>
